<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.2">
<l>tuṟantē ṉārvacceṟ ṟaccuṟṟan tuṟantamaiyāl</l>
<l>ciṟantēṉ niṉṉaṭikkē yaṭimaiti rumālē</l>
<l>aṟantā ṉāyttirivā yuṉṉaiyeṉ maṉattakattē</l>
<l>tiṟampā malkoṇṭēṉ tiruviṇṇa karāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I renounced the love [and] hate of relationships; by that renouncing,</l>
<l>I have succeeded in service at your feet, Tirumāl.</l>
<l>Without swerving, I have held you in the depths of my heart,</l>
<l>You who transforms to virtue itself, [Lord] of Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
